query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(mi_idx it2) NoMergeJoin(it2 mi_idx mc) NoMergeJoin(ct it2 mc mi_idx t) NoHashJoin(ct it2 mc mi_idx t cn) NoMergeJoin(cn ct it2 mc mi mi_idx t it1) */ select min(cn.name) AS movie_company,
min(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
min(t.title) AS drama_horror_movie
from movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
inner join info_type AS it2
on mi_idx.info_type_id = it2.id AND mi_idx.info > '6.5' AND it2.info = 'rating'
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on mc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
inner join company_type AS ct
on ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND ct.kind = 'production companies'
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1994 AND 2006
inner join company_name AS cn
on cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Western',
'Drama')
inner join info_type AS it1
on mi.info_type_id = it1.id AND it1.info = 'genres';
